# win-unique

Use `cargo doc --open` to see documentation

Need to run it as administrator.

Example:

```rust
use win_unique::COMLibrary;
use win_unique::{product, mdm_dev_detail_ext01};

fn main() {
    let _com_con = COMLibrary::new().unwrap(); // initialise security context

    println!("{:#?}\n{:#?}", product(), mdm_dev_detail_ext01());
}
```
